create.t.sol
└── when deploying a new adapter contract
    ├── when the owner is a non-zero address
    │   ├── it should return the correct adapter address
    │   ├── it should emit the AdapterCreated event
    │   ├── it should deploy the adapter at the correct deterministic address
    │   ├── it should revert with AdapterCreationFailed when deployment fails due to an existing contract
    │   └── it should revert when not enough gas is provided
    └── when the owner is the zero address
        └── it should revert with InvalidOwner
